<namelist_summary>
###############################################################################
namelist_ECS.xml

Description
Namelist to calculate the Equilibrium Climate Sensitivity (ECS) using
abrupt4xCO2 and piControl runs for the variables rtmt and tas. 

Authors
Ricarda Rettinger

Project
DLR ESMVal
CRESCENDO

Reference
Andrews et al., 2012, Forcing, feedbacks and climate sensitivity in CMIP5 
coupled atmosphere-ocean climate models, Geophysical Research Letters, 39.
DOI: 10.1029/2012GL051607

This namelist is part of the ESMValTool
###############################################################################
</namelist_summary>

<GLOBAL>
    <write_plots type="boolean">              True         </write_plots>
    <write_netcdf type="boolean">             True         </write_netcdf>
    <force_processing type="boolean">        False         </force_processing>
    <wrk_dir type="path">                    ./work/       </wrk_dir>
